Momos are the South Asian dumplings that are delicacy in Nepal and Tibet. Momos are flour dumplings filled with minced meat, chopped garlic, onions and spices, traditionally, and are served with spicy chattni (sauce). Its tasty and strong flavor, aromatic smell and juiciness makes it unique and wantful for your tastebuds.

Fillings served:
1. Minced Meat (Keema)
2. Chicken Chunks 
3. Veggie ( Cabbage/Potato/Mixed Vegetable/Vegie of your choice)

Chattnis served:
1. Tomato Chattni
2. Garlic and Green chili Chattni
3. Garlic and Red Chili Chattni
4. Mint Chattni
4. Coriander Chattni

Pricing:
1. Rs 150/plate  (6 dumplings with filling of your choice+Tomato chattni)
2. Rs 250/plate (12 dumplings with filling of your choice+chattni of your choie)
3. Rs 500 ( 30 dumplings with filling of your choice+3 chattnis of your choice)
